# NeuroScan AI — Frontend Environment
# Leave VITE_API_BASE empty for Railway deployment.
# The frontend and backend are served from the same URL,
# so relative path /api/v1 works automatically.
#
# Only set this if you are running the frontend standalone
# on a different port/domain from the backend:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
